---
title: Golden Beef Patties with Cream Cheese Smashed Potatoes and Aioli
description: Who doesn't love a good dip? Golden, mini beef patties and tender-crisp snap peas are extra delicious with a swipe of savoury garlic aioli.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/galettes-de-boeuf-dorees-433bb122.jpg
